---
title: North African Spiced Freekeh with Roasted Squash
description: Prepare for a hit of flavour and colour with this hearty veggie salad! Moroccan spiced roasted squash with harissa onions bring a robust and spicy flavour to this dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/freekeh-aux-epices-nord-africaines-9eb49546.jpg
